init_text: Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world has changed drastically in the last 50 years, and the real question remains: Why?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So, what does that mean for us as Christians?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think the advancement of technology has also caused many to be more connected with one another, but in a different way.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Like for example, after World War I and II we have worked so hard to make sure that the same mistakes are not made again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I personally think that technology has truly changed our world in a positive manner and I can't imagine what life would be like without all of
